        <p class="primary-standfirst">唐纳德·特朗普计划于2018年1月30日发表首次国情咨文演讲。那么何为国情咨文演讲？其对市场有何影响？</p>

                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="global-component parbase section">





<div class="global-component">
    
    
        
            
                
                    
                        <div class="new-content-component">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            bg-none 
            image-layout-full-bottom
            
            
            content-no-padding
            text-position-top
            text-no-image
